{
  "book": "2nephi",
  "bookName": "2 Nephi",
  "chapter": 4,
  "voice": {
    "provider": "elevenlabs",
    "voice_id": "iJpuSZDxZSBJHFSeavba",
    "model_id": "eleven_multilingual_v2",
    "settings": {
      "stability": 0.5,
      "similarity_boost": 0.75,
      "style": 0.35,
      "use_speaker_boost": true
    },
    "name": "sister-m"
  },
  "pauses": {
    "line_ms": 180,
    "verse_ms": 500
  },
  "duration": 573.503,
  "lines": [
    {
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 4.69,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And now, I, Nephi, speak concerning the prophecies",
      "verse": "4:1",
      "lineIndex": 1
    },
    {
      "start": 4.87,
      "end": 7.192,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "of which my father hath spoken,",
      "verse": "4:1",
      "lineIndex": 2
    },
    {
      "start": 7.372,
      "end": 10.994,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "concerning Joseph, who was carried into Egypt.",
      "verse": "4:1",
      "lineIndex": 3
    },
    {
      "start": 11.674,
      "end": 15.946,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "For behold, he truly prophesied concerning all his seed.",
      "verse": "4:2",
      "lineIndex": 4
    },
    {
      "start": 16.126,
      "end": 21.745,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And the prophecies which he wrote,",
      "verse": "4:2",
      "lineIndex": 5
    },
    {
      "start": 21.925,
      "end": 23.643,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "there are not many greater.",
      "verse": "4:2",
      "lineIndex": 6
    },
    {
      "start": 23.823,
      "end": 26.052,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And he prophesied concerning us,",
      "verse": "4:2",
      "lineIndex": 7
    },
    {
      "start": 26.232,
      "end": 28.275,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and our future generations;",
      "verse": "4:2",
      "lineIndex": 8
    },
    {
      "start": 28.455,
      "end": 31.892,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and they are written upon the plates of brass.",
      "verse": "4:2",
      "lineIndex": 9
    },
    {
      "start": 32.572,
      "end": 36.334,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Wherefore, after my father had made an end of speaking",
      "verse": "4:3",
      "lineIndex": 10
    },
    {
      "start": 36.514,
      "end": 38.882,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "concerning the prophecies of Joseph,",
      "verse": "4:3",
      "lineIndex": 11
    },
    {
      "start": 39.062,
      "end": 41.57,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "he called the children of Laman,",
      "verse": "4:3",
      "lineIndex": 12
    },
    {
      "start": 41.75,
      "end": 44.769,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "his sons, and his daughters,",
      "verse": "4:3",
      "lineIndex": 13
    },
    {
      "start": 44.949,
      "end": 46.574,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and said unto them:",
      "verse": "4:3",
      "lineIndex": 14
    },
    {
      "start": 46.754,
      "end": 49.865,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Behold, my sons, and my daughters,",
      "verse": "4:3",
      "lineIndex": 15
    },
    {
      "start": 50.045,
      "end": 53.807,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "who are the sons and the daughters of my firstborn,",
      "verse": "4:3",
      "lineIndex": 16
    },
    {
      "start": 53.987,
      "end": 57.284,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I would that ye should give ear unto my words.",
      "verse": "4:3",
      "lineIndex": 17
    },
    {
      "start": 57.964,
      "end": 60.193,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "For the Lord God hath said that:",
      "verse": "4:4",
      "lineIndex": 18
    },
    {
      "start": 60.373,
      "end": 63.577,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Inasmuch as ye shall keep my commandments",
      "verse": "4:4",
      "lineIndex": 19
    },
    {
      "start": 63.757,
      "end": 65.893,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "ye shall prosper in the land;",
      "verse": "4:4",
      "lineIndex": 20
    },
    {
      "start": 66.073,
      "end": 70.253,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and inasmuch as ye will not keep my commandments",
      "verse": "4:4",
      "lineIndex": 21
    },
    {
      "start": 70.433,
      "end": 73.127,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "ye shall be cut off from my presence.",
      "verse": "4:4",
      "lineIndex": 22
    },
    {
      "start": 73.807,
      "end": 76.965,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "But behold, my sons and my daughters,",
      "verse": "4:5",
      "lineIndex": 24
    },
    {
      "start": 77.145,
      "end": 79.095,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I cannot go down to my grave",
      "verse": "4:5",
      "lineIndex": 25
    },
    {
      "start": 79.275,
      "end": 81.69,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "save I should leave a blessing upon you;",
      "verse": "4:5",
      "lineIndex": 26
    },
    {
      "start": 81.87,
      "end": 86.56,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for behold, I know that if ye are brought up in the way ye should go",
      "verse": "4:5",
      "lineIndex": 27
    },
    {
      "start": 86.74,
      "end": 88.876,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "ye will not depart from it.",
      "verse": "4:5",
      "lineIndex": 28
    },
    {
      "start": 89.556,
      "end": 91.785,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Wherefore, if ye are cursed,",
      "verse": "4:6",
      "lineIndex": 29
    },
    {
      "start": 91.965,
      "end": 95.309,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "behold, I leave my blessing upon you,",
      "verse": "4:6",
      "lineIndex": 30
    },
    {
      "start": 95.489,
      "end": 97.997,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that the cursing may be taken from you",
      "verse": "4:6",
      "lineIndex": 31
    },
    {
      "start": 98.177,
      "end": 101.474,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and be answered upon the heads of your parents.",
      "verse": "4:6",
      "lineIndex": 32
    },
    {
      "start": 102.154,
      "end": 104.43,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Wherefore, because of my blessing",
      "verse": "4:7",
      "lineIndex": 33
    },
    {
      "start": 104.61,
      "end": 108.557,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "the Lord God will not suffer that ye shall perish;",
      "verse": "4:7",
      "lineIndex": 34
    },
    {
      "start": 108.737,
      "end": 111.709,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "wherefore, he will be merciful unto you",
      "verse": "4:7",
      "lineIndex": 35
    },
    {
      "start": 111.889,
      "end": 114.211,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and unto your seed forever.",
      "verse": "4:7",
      "lineIndex": 36
    },
    {
      "start": 114.891,
      "end": 119.907,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that after my father had made an end of speaking",
      "verse": "4:8",
      "lineIndex": 37
    },
    {
      "start": 120.087,
      "end": 122.409,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "to the sons and daughters of Laman,",
      "verse": "4:8",
      "lineIndex": 38
    },
    {
      "start": 122.589,
      "end": 127.094,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "he caused the sons and daughters of Lemuel to be brought before him.",
      "verse": "4:8",
      "lineIndex": 39
    },
    {
      "start": 127.774,
      "end": 130.096,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And he spake unto them, saying:",
      "verse": "4:9",
      "lineIndex": 40
    },
    {
      "start": 130.276,
      "end": 133.573,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Behold, my sons and my daughters,",
      "verse": "4:9",
      "lineIndex": 41
    },
    {
      "start": 133.753,
      "end": 137.608,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "who are the sons and the daughters of my second son;",
      "verse": "4:9",
      "lineIndex": 42
    },
    {
      "start": 137.788,
      "end": 141.735,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "behold I leave unto you the same blessing",
      "verse": "4:9",
      "lineIndex": 43
    },
    {
      "start": 141.915,
      "end": 145.77,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which I left unto the sons and daughters of Laman;",
      "verse": "4:9",
      "lineIndex": 44
    },
    {
      "start": 145.95,
      "end": 149.247,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "wherefore, thou shalt not utterly be destroyed;",
      "verse": "4:9",
      "lineIndex": 45
    },
    {
      "start": 149.427,
      "end": 152.631,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "but in the end thy seed shall be blessed.",
      "verse": "4:9",
      "lineIndex": 46
    },
    {
      "start": 153.311,
      "end": 158.419,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that when my father had made an end of speaking unto them,",
      "verse": "4:10",
      "lineIndex": 47
    },
    {
      "start": 158.599,
      "end": 162.175,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "behold, he spake unto the sons of Ishmael,",
      "verse": "4:10",
      "lineIndex": 48
    },
    {
      "start": 162.355,
      "end": 165.699,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yea, and even all his household.",
      "verse": "4:10",
      "lineIndex": 49
    },
    {
      "start": 166.379,
      "end": 170.094,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And after he had made an end of speaking unto them,",
      "verse": "4:11",
      "lineIndex": 50
    },
    {
      "start": 170.274,
      "end": 172.224,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "he spake unto Sam, saying:",
      "verse": "4:11",
      "lineIndex": 51
    },
    {
      "start": 172.404,
      "end": 175.237,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Blessed art thou, and thy seed;",
      "verse": "4:11",
      "lineIndex": 52
    },
    {
      "start": 175.417,
      "end": 180.154,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for thou shalt inherit the land like unto thy brother Nephi.",
      "verse": "4:11",
      "lineIndex": 53
    },
    {
      "start": 180.334,
      "end": 183.492,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And thy seed shall be numbered with his seed;",
      "verse": "4:11",
      "lineIndex": 54
    },
    {
      "start": 183.672,
      "end": 186.783,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and thou shalt be even like unto thy brother,",
      "verse": "4:11",
      "lineIndex": 55
    },
    {
      "start": 186.963,
      "end": 189.703,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and thy seed like unto his seed;",
      "verse": "4:11",
      "lineIndex": 56
    },
    {
      "start": 189.883,
      "end": 193.087,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and thou shalt be blessed in all thy days.",
      "verse": "4:11",
      "lineIndex": 57
    },
    {
      "start": 193.767,
      "end": 199.758,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass after my father, Lehi, had spoken unto all his household,",
      "verse": "4:12",
      "lineIndex": 58
    },
    {
      "start": 199.938,
      "end": 205.325,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "according to the feelings of his heart and the Spirit of the Lord which was in him,",
      "verse": "4:12",
      "lineIndex": 59
    },
    {
      "start": 205.505,
      "end": 210.428,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "he waxed old. And it came to pass that he died, and was buried.",
      "verse": "4:12",
      "lineIndex": 60
    },
    {
      "start": 211.108,
      "end": 215.148,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that not many days after his death,",
      "verse": "4:13",
      "lineIndex": 61
    },
    {
      "start": 215.328,
      "end": 217.046,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Laman and Lemuel",
      "verse": "4:13",
      "lineIndex": 62
    },
    {
      "start": 217.226,
      "end": 220.57,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the sons of Ishmael were angry with me",
      "verse": "4:13",
      "lineIndex": 63
    },
    {
      "start": 220.75,
      "end": 223.444,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "because of the admonitions of the Lord.",
      "verse": "4:13",
      "lineIndex": 64
    },
    {
      "start": 224.124,
      "end": 228.629,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "For I, Nephi, was constrained to speak unto them,",
      "verse": "4:14",
      "lineIndex": 65
    },
    {
      "start": 228.809,
      "end": 230.481,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "according to his word;",
      "verse": "4:14",
      "lineIndex": 66
    },
    {
      "start": 230.661,
      "end": 233.54,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for I had spoken many things unto them,",
      "verse": "4:14",
      "lineIndex": 67
    },
    {
      "start": 233.72,
      "end": 236.646,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also my father, before his death;",
      "verse": "4:14",
      "lineIndex": 68
    },
    {
      "start": 236.826,
      "end": 240.681,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "many of which sayings are written upon mine other plates;",
      "verse": "4:14",
      "lineIndex": 69
    },
    {
      "start": 240.861,
      "end": 244.762,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for a more history part are written upon mine other plates.",
      "verse": "4:14",
      "lineIndex": 70
    },
    {
      "start": 245.442,
      "end": 248.646,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And upon these I write the things of my soul,",
      "verse": "4:15",
      "lineIndex": 72
    },
    {
      "start": 248.826,
      "end": 250.684,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and many of the scriptures",
      "verse": "4:15",
      "lineIndex": 73
    },
    {
      "start": 250.864,
      "end": 253.558,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which are engraven upon the plates of brass.",
      "verse": "4:15",
      "lineIndex": 74
    },
    {
      "start": 253.738,
      "end": 256.757,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "For my soul delighteth in the scriptures,",
      "verse": "4:15",
      "lineIndex": 75
    },
    {
      "start": 256.937,
      "end": 259.166,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and my heart pondereth them,",
      "verse": "4:15",
      "lineIndex": 76
    },
    {
      "start": 259.346,
      "end": 263.758,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and writeth them for the learning and the profit of my children.",
      "verse": "4:15",
      "lineIndex": 77
    },
    {
      "start": 264.438,
      "end": 268.432,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Behold, my soul delighteth in the things of the Lord;",
      "verse": "4:16",
      "lineIndex": 78
    },
    {
      "start": 268.612,
      "end": 272.467,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and my heart pondereth continually upon the things",
      "verse": "4:16",
      "lineIndex": 79
    },
    {
      "start": 272.647,
      "end": 274.644,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which I have seen and heard.",
      "verse": "4:16",
      "lineIndex": 80
    },
    {
      "start": 275.324,
      "end": 279.782,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Nevertheless, notwithstanding the great goodness of the Lord,",
      "verse": "4:17",
      "lineIndex": 81
    },
    {
      "start": 279.962,
      "end": 283.399,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "in showing me his great and marvelous works,",
      "verse": "4:17",
      "lineIndex": 82
    },
    {
      "start": 283.579,
      "end": 285.297,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "my heart exclaimeth:",
      "verse": "4:17",
      "lineIndex": 83
    },
    {
      "start": 285.477,
      "end": 287.427,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "O wretched man that I am!",
      "verse": "4:17",
      "lineIndex": 84
    },
    {
      "start": 287.607,
      "end": 290.997,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Yea, my heart sorroweth because of my flesh;",
      "verse": "4:17",
      "lineIndex": 85
    },
    {
      "start": 291.177,
      "end": 294.428,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "my soul grieveth because of mine iniquities.",
      "verse": "4:17",
      "lineIndex": 86
    },
    {
      "start": 295.108,
      "end": 296.826,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I am encompassed about,",
      "verse": "4:18",
      "lineIndex": 87
    },
    {
      "start": 297.006,
      "end": 300.257,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "because of the temptations and the sins",
      "verse": "4:18",
      "lineIndex": 88
    },
    {
      "start": 300.437,
      "end": 302.62,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which do so easily beset me.",
      "verse": "4:18",
      "lineIndex": 89
    },
    {
      "start": 303.3,
      "end": 305.576,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And when I desire to rejoice,",
      "verse": "4:19",
      "lineIndex": 90
    },
    {
      "start": 305.756,
      "end": 308.682,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "my heart groaneth because of my sins;",
      "verse": "4:19",
      "lineIndex": 91
    },
    {
      "start": 308.862,
      "end": 312.484,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "nevertheless, I know in whom I have trusted.",
      "verse": "4:19",
      "lineIndex": 92
    },
    {
      "start": 313.164,
      "end": 315.3,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "My God hath been my support;",
      "verse": "4:20",
      "lineIndex": 93
    },
    {
      "start": 315.48,
      "end": 316.873,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "he hath led me",
      "verse": "4:20",
      "lineIndex": 94
    },
    {
      "start": 317.053,
      "end": 319.747,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "through mine afflictions in the wilderness;",
      "verse": "4:20",
      "lineIndex": 95
    },
    {
      "start": 319.927,
      "end": 321.785,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and he hath preserved me",
      "verse": "4:20",
      "lineIndex": 96
    },
    {
      "start": 321.965,
      "end": 324.798,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "upon the waters of the great deep.",
      "verse": "4:20",
      "lineIndex": 97
    },
    {
      "start": 325.478,
      "end": 327.661,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "He hath filled me with his love,",
      "verse": "4:21",
      "lineIndex": 98
    },
    {
      "start": 327.841,
      "end": 330.813,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "even unto the consuming of my flesh.",
      "verse": "4:21",
      "lineIndex": 99
    },
    {
      "start": 331.493,
      "end": 333.722,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "He hath confounded mine enemies,",
      "verse": "4:22",
      "lineIndex": 100
    },
    {
      "start": 333.902,
      "end": 337.06,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "unto the causing of them to quake before me.",
      "verse": "4:22",
      "lineIndex": 101
    },
    {
      "start": 337.74,
      "end": 340.851,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Behold, he hath heard my cry by day,",
      "verse": "4:23",
      "lineIndex": 102
    },
    {
      "start": 341.031,
      "end": 343.167,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and he hath given me knowledge",
      "verse": "4:23",
      "lineIndex": 103
    },
    {
      "start": 343.347,
      "end": 345.437,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "by visions in the night-time.",
      "verse": "4:23",
      "lineIndex": 104
    },
    {
      "start": 346.117,
      "end": 348.903,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And by day have I waxed bold",
      "verse": "4:24",
      "lineIndex": 105
    },
    {
      "start": 349.083,
      "end": 351.173,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "in mighty prayer before him;",
      "verse": "4:24",
      "lineIndex": 106
    },
    {
      "start": 351.353,
      "end": 354.372,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yea, my voice have I sent up on high;",
      "verse": "4:24",
      "lineIndex": 107
    },
    {
      "start": 354.552,
      "end": 357.989,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and angels came down and ministered unto me.",
      "verse": "4:24",
      "lineIndex": 108
    },
    {
      "start": 358.669,
      "end": 360.991,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And upon the wings of his Spirit",
      "verse": "4:25",
      "lineIndex": 110
    },
    {
      "start": 361.171,
      "end": 363.307,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "hath my body been carried away",
      "verse": "4:25",
      "lineIndex": 111
    },
    {
      "start": 363.487,
      "end": 365.902,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "upon exceedingly high mountains.",
      "verse": "4:25",
      "lineIndex": 112
    },
    {
      "start": 366.082,
      "end": 369.147,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And mine eyes have beheld great things,",
      "verse": "4:25",
      "lineIndex": 113
    },
    {
      "start": 369.327,
      "end": 371.881,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yea, even too great for man;",
      "verse": "4:25",
      "lineIndex": 114
    },
    {
      "start": 372.061,
      "end": 375.637,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "therefore I was bidden that I should not write them.",
      "verse": "4:25",
      "lineIndex": 115
    },
    {
      "start": 376.317,
      "end": 379.103,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "O then, if I have seen so great things,",
      "verse": "4:26",
      "lineIndex": 116
    },
    {
      "start": 379.283,
      "end": 383.741,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "if the Lord in his condescension unto the children of men",
      "verse": "4:26",
      "lineIndex": 117
    },
    {
      "start": 383.921,
      "end": 386.847,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "hath visited men in so much mercy,",
      "verse": "4:26",
      "lineIndex": 118
    },
    {
      "start": 387.027,
      "end": 388.977,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "why should my heart weep",
      "verse": "4:26",
      "lineIndex": 119
    },
    {
      "start": 389.157,
      "end": 392.547,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and my soul linger in the valley of sorrow,",
      "verse": "4:26",
      "lineIndex": 120
    },
    {
      "start": 392.727,
      "end": 394.817,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and my flesh waste away,",
      "verse": "4:26",
      "lineIndex": 121
    },
    {
      "start": 394.997,
      "end": 396.622,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and my strength slacken,",
      "verse": "4:26",
      "lineIndex": 122
    },
    {
      "start": 396.802,
      "end": 398.613,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "because of mine afflictions?",
      "verse": "4:26",
      "lineIndex": 123
    },
    {
      "start": 399.293,
      "end": 401.615,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And why should I yield to sin,",
      "verse": "4:27",
      "lineIndex": 124
    },
    {
      "start": 401.795,
      "end": 403.56,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "because of my flesh?",
      "verse": "4:27",
      "lineIndex": 125
    },
    {
      "start": 403.74,
      "end": 407.177,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Yea, why should I give way to temptations,",
      "verse": "4:27",
      "lineIndex": 126
    },
    {
      "start": 407.357,
      "end": 416.877,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that the evil one have place in my heart",
      "verse": "4:27",
      "lineIndex": 127
    },
    {
      "start": 417.057,
      "end": 420.308,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "to destroy my peace and afflict my soul?",
      "verse": "4:27",
      "lineIndex": 128
    },
    {
      "start": 420.488,
      "end": 422.996,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Why am I angry because of mine enemy?",
      "verse": "4:27",
      "lineIndex": 129
    },
    {
      "start": 423.676,
      "end": 425.255,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Awake, my soul!",
      "verse": "4:28",
      "lineIndex": 130
    },
    {
      "start": 425.435,
      "end": 427.432,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "No longer droop in sin.",
      "verse": "4:28",
      "lineIndex": 131
    },
    {
      "start": 427.612,
      "end": 429.655,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Rejoice, O my heart,",
      "verse": "4:28",
      "lineIndex": 132
    },
    {
      "start": 429.835,
      "end": 433.875,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and give place no more for the enemy of my soul.",
      "verse": "4:28",
      "lineIndex": 133
    },
    {
      "start": 434.555,
      "end": 436.459,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Do not anger again",
      "verse": "4:29",
      "lineIndex": 134
    },
    {
      "start": 436.639,
      "end": 438.357,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "because of mine enemies.",
      "verse": "4:29",
      "lineIndex": 135
    },
    {
      "start": 438.537,
      "end": 440.72,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Do not slacken my strength",
      "verse": "4:29",
      "lineIndex": 136
    },
    {
      "start": 440.9,
      "end": 442.758,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "because of mine afflictions.",
      "verse": "4:29",
      "lineIndex": 137
    },
    {
      "start": 443.438,
      "end": 445.481,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Rejoice, O my heart,",
      "verse": "4:30",
      "lineIndex": 138
    },
    {
      "start": 445.661,
      "end": 448.215,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and cry unto the Lord, and say:",
      "verse": "4:30",
      "lineIndex": 139
    },
    {
      "start": 448.395,
      "end": 451.089,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "O Lord, I will praise thee forever;",
      "verse": "4:30",
      "lineIndex": 140
    },
    {
      "start": 451.269,
      "end": 454.102,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yea, my soul will rejoice in thee,",
      "verse": "4:30",
      "lineIndex": 141
    },
    {
      "start": 454.282,
      "end": 457.719,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "my God, and the rock of my salvation.",
      "verse": "4:30",
      "lineIndex": 142
    },
    {
      "start": 458.399,
      "end": 459.281,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "O Lord,",
      "verse": "4:31",
      "lineIndex": 143
    },
    {
      "start": 459.461,
      "end": 461.272,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "wilt thou redeem my soul?",
      "verse": "4:31",
      "lineIndex": 144
    },
    {
      "start": 461.452,
      "end": 464.935,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Wilt thou deliver me out of the hands of mine enemies?",
      "verse": "4:31",
      "lineIndex": 145
    },
    {
      "start": 465.115,
      "end": 469.573,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Wilt thou make me that I may shake at the appearance of sin?",
      "verse": "4:31",
      "lineIndex": 146
    },
    {
      "start": 470.253,
      "end": 472.111,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "May the gates of hell",
      "verse": "4:32",
      "lineIndex": 147
    },
    {
      "start": 472.291,
      "end": 474.706,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "be shut continually before me,",
      "verse": "4:32",
      "lineIndex": 148
    },
    {
      "start": 474.886,
      "end": 477.022,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "because that my heart is broken",
      "verse": "4:32",
      "lineIndex": 149
    },
    {
      "start": 477.202,
      "end": 479.292,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and my spirit is contrite!",
      "verse": "4:32",
      "lineIndex": 150
    },
    {
      "start": 479.472,
      "end": 482.351,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "O Lord, wilt thou not shut",
      "verse": "4:32",
      "lineIndex": 151
    },
    {
      "start": 482.531,
      "end": 485.503,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "the gates of thy righteousness before me,",
      "verse": "4:32",
      "lineIndex": 152
    },
    {
      "start": 485.683,
      "end": 489.166,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that I may walk in the path of the low valley,",
      "verse": "4:32",
      "lineIndex": 153
    },
    {
      "start": 489.346,
      "end": 491.947,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that I may be strict in the plain road!",
      "verse": "4:32",
      "lineIndex": 154
    },
    {
      "start": 492.627,
      "end": 493.509,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "O Lord,",
      "verse": "4:33",
      "lineIndex": 155
    },
    {
      "start": 493.689,
      "end": 495.686,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "wilt thou encircle me around",
      "verse": "4:33",
      "lineIndex": 156
    },
    {
      "start": 495.866,
      "end": 497.816,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "in the robe of thy righteousness!",
      "verse": "4:33",
      "lineIndex": 157
    },
    {
      "start": 497.996,
      "end": 498.878,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "O Lord,",
      "verse": "4:33",
      "lineIndex": 158
    },
    {
      "start": 499.058,
      "end": 503.33,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "wilt thou make a way for mine escape before mine enemies!",
      "verse": "4:33",
      "lineIndex": 159
    },
    {
      "start": 503.51,
      "end": 506.389,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Wilt thou make my path straight before me!",
      "verse": "4:33",
      "lineIndex": 160
    },
    {
      "start": 506.569,
      "end": 512.699,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Wilt thou not place a stumbling block in my way\u2014",
      "verse": "4:33",
      "lineIndex": 161
    },
    {
      "start": 512.879,
      "end": 515.712,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "but that thou wouldst clear my way before me,",
      "verse": "4:33",
      "lineIndex": 162
    },
    {
      "start": 515.892,
      "end": 520.397,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and hedge not up my way, but the ways of mine enemy.",
      "verse": "4:33",
      "lineIndex": 163
    },
    {
      "start": 521.077,
      "end": 521.959,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "O Lord,",
      "verse": "4:34",
      "lineIndex": 164
    },
    {
      "start": 522.139,
      "end": 523.672,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I have trusted in thee,",
      "verse": "4:34",
      "lineIndex": 165
    },
    {
      "start": 523.852,
      "end": 526.453,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I will trust in thee forever.",
      "verse": "4:34",
      "lineIndex": 166
    },
    {
      "start": 526.633,
      "end": 530.209,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I will not put my trust in the arm of flesh;",
      "verse": "4:34",
      "lineIndex": 167
    },
    {
      "start": 530.389,
      "end": 533.454,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for I know that cursed is he",
      "verse": "4:34",
      "lineIndex": 168
    },
    {
      "start": 533.634,
      "end": 536.931,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that putteth his trust in the arm of flesh.",
      "verse": "4:34",
      "lineIndex": 169
    },
    {
      "start": 537.111,
      "end": 542.405,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Yea, cursed is he that putteth his trust in man",
      "verse": "4:34",
      "lineIndex": 170
    },
    {
      "start": 542.585,
      "end": 544.535,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "or maketh flesh his arm.",
      "verse": "4:34",
      "lineIndex": 171
    },
    {
      "start": 545.215,
      "end": 550.231,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Yea, I know that God will give liberally to him that asketh.",
      "verse": "4:35",
      "lineIndex": 172
    },
    {
      "start": 550.411,
      "end": 553.29,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Yea, my God will give me,",
      "verse": "4:35",
      "lineIndex": 173
    },
    {
      "start": 553.47,
      "end": 555.281,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "if I ask not amiss;",
      "verse": "4:35",
      "lineIndex": 174
    },
    {
      "start": 555.461,
      "end": 558.898,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "therefore I will lift up my voice unto thee;",
      "verse": "4:35",
      "lineIndex": 175
    },
    {
      "start": 559.078,
      "end": 561.214,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yea, I will cry unto thee,",
      "verse": "4:35",
      "lineIndex": 176
    },
    {
      "start": 561.394,
      "end": 564.134,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "my God, the rock of my righteousness.",
      "verse": "4:35",
      "lineIndex": 177
    },
    {
      "start": 564.314,
      "end": 568.494,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Behold, my voice shall forever ascend up unto thee,",
      "verse": "4:35",
      "lineIndex": 178
    },
    {
      "start": 568.674,
      "end": 571.832,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "my rock and mine everlasting God.",
      "verse": "4:35",
      "lineIndex": 179
    },
    {
      "start": 572.012,
      "end": 572.848,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Amen.",
      "verse": "4:35",
      "lineIndex": 180
    }
  ]
}